    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nLooking for a pilot to run a couple packages -\n\nPACKAGES FOR PICK UP (ANY ORDER)\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item1|SerialNumber)</EM4> from the <EM4>~mission(Pickup1|Address)</EM4>\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item2|SerialNumber)</EM4> from the <EM4>~mission(Pickup2|Address)</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item1|SerialNumber)</EM4> to the <EM4>~mission(Dropoff1|Address)</EM4>\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item2|SerialNumber)</EM4> to the <EM4>~mission(Dropoff2|Address)</EM4>\n\nNeed it done quick and without screwups. And don't forget to pack a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to bring along. \n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)",
